<span class="blogText bigText"><div class="bpBody"><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% transparent; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-moz-background-clip: border; -moz-background-origin: padding; -moz-background-size: auto auto; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="blogText bigText"><span style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% transparent; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-moz-background-clip: border; -moz-background-origin: padding; -moz-background-size: auto auto; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">(Kyodo News / Associated Press)</span></span></span></div><br />
<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% transparent; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-moz-background-clip: border; -moz-background-origin: padding; -moz-background-size: auto auto; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">Un terremoto de magnitud 8.9 golpeó la costa NorEste de Japón la madrugada de hoy día 11 de Marzo.</span> <span style="-moz-background-clip: border; -moz-background-origin: padding; -moz-background-size: auto auto; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">El  terremoto - uno de las más grandes de la historia, provocó un tsunami  con olas de más de 10 metros que arrasó la costa Este del país, matando a cientos de personas y  arrastrando a su paso coches, casas, edificios y barcos.</span>..como en todas las catástrofes...me quedo muda ante tanta desolación....</span></div></div></span><span class="blogText bigText"><div class="bpBody"><span style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% transparent; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-moz-background-clip: border; -moz-background-origin: padding; -moz-background-size: auto auto; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;"></span></span><i></i><span style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% transparent; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-moz-background-clip: border; -moz-background-origin: padding; -moz-background-size: auto auto; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;"> ( </span></span><a href="http://www.boston.com/bigpicture/2011/03/massive_earthquake_hits_japan.html"><span style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% transparent; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-moz-background-clip: border; -moz-background-origin: padding; -moz-background-size: auto auto; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;">43 total de fotos</span></span></a><span style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% transparent; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-moz-background-clip: border; -moz-background-origin: padding; -moz-background-size: auto auto; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; border: 0pt none; display: inline; font-size: 100%; margin: 0pt; outline: 0pt none; padding: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline;"> )</span></span></div></span><br />
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-dwlzBcZ1K8E/TXp79-5ZCUI/AAAAAAAAeus/F1BHWCbI_I0/s1600/bp5.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="490" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-dwlzBcZ1K8E/TXp79-5ZCUI/AAAAAAAAeus/F1BHWCbI_I0/s640/bp5.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-dCk5rrlSEhQ/TXp8LJhrKgI/AAAAAAAAeu4/Lh1EikuSeiM/s1600/bp3.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="366" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-dCk5rrlSEhQ/TXp8LJhrKgI/AAAAAAAAeu4/Lh1EikuSeiM/s640/bp3.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-p4JW5tVHMW8/TXp8GSsdHsI/AAAAAAAAeu0/Vi2CLNmGeBQ/s1600/bp2.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="412" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-p4JW5tVHMW8/TXp8GSsdHsI/AAAAAAAAeu0/Vi2CLNmGeBQ/s640/bp2.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-5iyMYSxcr8c/TXp8BMVlEBI/AAAAAAAAeuw/v9Ci1Ab__CI/s1600/bp4.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="428" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-5iyMYSxcr8c/TXp8BMVlEBI/AAAAAAAAeuw/v9Ci1Ab__CI/s640/bp4.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-Ky7dizEKNYw/TXp72dlHj6I/AAAAAAAAeuo/Qp1RjQkqKzI/s1600/bp6.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="408" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-Ky7dizEKNYw/TXp72dlHj6I/AAAAAAAAeuo/Qp1RjQkqKzI/s640/bp6.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><