y por eso quiero regalar a tod@s los amig@s, y seguidores esta</b></span></i><br />
<div style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;"><i><span style="font-size: large;"><b></b></span></i><i><span style="font-size: large;"><b></b></span></i></div><div style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;"><i><span style="font-size: large;"><b> <u><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="color: blue;">Felicitación Navideña</span></span></u>&nbsp;</b></span></i></div><div style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;"><i><span style="font-size: large;"><b> junto con mis </b></span></i><i><span style="font-size: large;"><b>mejores deseos para el</b></span></i></div><div style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;"><i><span style="font-size: large;"><b></b></span></i></div><div style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;"><i><span style="font-size: large;"><b> <span style="color: #bf9000; font-size: x-large;"><u>Año 2011</u></span></b></span></i></div><div style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;"><i><span style="font-size: large;"><b><span style="color: #bf9000; font-size: x-large;"><u> </u></span></b></span></i></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_Qu-KxwZh9G4/TPlUswvsGdI/AAAAAAAAbWc/Vowz0mZqsHI/s1600/FotoFlexer_Animation.gif" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="442" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_Qu-KxwZh9G4/TPlUswvsGdI/AAAAAAAAbWc/Vowz0mZqsHI/s640/FotoFlexer_Animation.gif" width="640" /></a></div><a href="http://www.jacquielawson.com/preview.asp?cont=1&amp;hdn=0&amp;pv=3175361&amp;path=83563"><i><span style="font-size: large;"><b>Pinchar aquí...</b></span></i></a></div><div style="text-align: left;"><i><span style="font-size: large;"><b>y  cuando se abra la postal, sólo teneís que seguir las indicaciones de la pantalla...así qu